# 🏨 Hotel Booking Analysis Dashboard (Excel)

## 📌 Objective
To analyze hotel booking data and visualize booking trends, cancellation reasons, and customer preferences using Excel.

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Conditional Formatting
- Charts and Dashboards

## 📊 Key Features
- Booking status summary
- Cancellation reason trends
- Monthly and region-wise booking patterns
- Interactive dashboard with filters

## 📌 Insights
- Most cancellations occurred in the city hotel segment.
- Repeated guests had a lower cancellation rate.

## 🧑‍💻 About Me
This project helped me demonstrate Excel dashboarding and visualization skills in a real-world hospitality dataset.
